snippet.title: GUNDAM BREAKER 4 - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Break, Build & Battle like never before! Build your personal Gunpla with parts from a huge collection of kits, and deepest customization options.

Put your build to the test with robust, frenetic combat. Show off your build in stunning detail with the new Diorama mode. All in GUNDAM BREAKER 4!

Coming to Nintendo Switch, PlayStation 4|5, & Steam in 2024 PRE-ORDER NOW https://bnent.eu/GundamBreaker4 #Gundam #Breaker #GB4
